item.title: CVE-2021-24391|2024-08-03T19:28:23.814Z -- unknown -- cashtomer
item.description: An editid GET parameter of the Cashtomer WordPress plugin through 1.0.0 is not properly sanitised, escaped or validated before inserting to a SQL statement, leading to SQL injection.
